To install this package use:

python setup.py install

If you do not have root access the following should work:

python setup.py install --user

The installation will then end up in the ~/.local folder

WARNING: the setup uses the distribute_setup package which requires an internet
connection. If you do not have an internet connection, in the setup.py script,
comment out the following lines:

from distribute_setup import use_setuptools
use_setuptools()
